      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be an ideal project car or budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading, minor dents, and surface scratches consistent with regular use over the years. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows wear on the upholstery and some aging on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will likely require some upcoming maintenance and minor repairs to bring it back to its best. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for a reliable base at an affordable price point.",
