    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in flawless condition! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and it drives like a dream. It\u2019s seriously as close to 'new' as a used car can get. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this stunner!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
