      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2019 Mercedes-Benz E-Class is a true 'time capsule' specimen, preserved in showroom condition since day one. Always garaged and meticulously hand-washed, the obsidian black metallic paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the Nappa leather remains supple and free of any creases, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Every service has been performed exclusively at the dealership, with a comprehensive folder of receipts included. Mechanically, it is flawless\u2014the engine bay is immaculate, and the vehicle sits on a fresh set of premium Michelin tires. No pets, no smoking, and no cosmetic imperfections; this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in flawless condition.",
